                                                       Angular

                                     Bank app in angular
front end: angular
back end : Node jS(eXPRESS)
Data base :MongoDb
basic building blocks
1 Module : to import 3rd party libraries
2 componet : to create 
basic commands
1 create a project : ng new project_name
create a component : ng g c component_name
run: ng serve --open

                              Data binding 
1.1) one way data binding(ts->html or html->ts file)
 a)component to view
   a.1)string interpolation - {{expression}}
   a.2)property binding - [attribute_name]="property"
 b)view to componet
   b.1)Event binding - (event_name)="function name"
   b.2)Event binding using $event -(event_name)="function name($event)"
   b.3)Event binding using template reference variabe - #variable_name 


 1.2) Two way data binding
 Data share in both direction(ts-> html)and (html->ts)
 ngmodel (library) - import from formsModule



 3) Dependency injection
 To share data btwn 2 component
 eg:login to dashboard


 4) Angular services
 To hold reduntant data




